{{Infobox Union |name= CDLS |country= [[San Marino]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= |full_name= Democratic Confederation of San Marino Workers |native_name= Confederazione Democratica dei Lavoratori Sammarinesi |image= [[File:CDLS logo.png]] |founded= November 12, 1957 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Domagnano]], San Marino |people= [[Marco Beccari]], secretary general |website= [http://www.cdls.sm www.cdls.sm] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Democratic Confederation of San Marino Workers''' (CDLS) is a [[national trade union center]] in [[San Marino]]. It was formed November 12, 1957 and is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
==Leadership== Secretary general: * [[Marino Bugli]] (1960–1969) * [[Giancarlo Ghironzi]] (1969–1971) * [[Antonio Zanotti]] (1971–1972) * [[Giovanni Giardi]] (1972–1984) * [[Antonio Macina]] (1984–1987) * [[Rita Ghironzi]] (1987–1991) * [[Marco Beccari]] (1991-current)
==Federations== The CDLS consists of four federations of workers as well as the [[Pensioners' Federation (CDLS)|Pensioners' Federation]] (Federazione Pensionati). * [[Industry Workers' Federation (CDLS)|Industry Workers' Federation]] (Federazione dei Lavoratori dell’Industria) * [[State Workers' Federation (CDLS)|State Workers' Federation]] (Federazione Pubblico Impiego) * [[Building Workers' Federation (CDLS)|Building Workers' Federation]] (Federazione Lavoratori delle Costruzioni) * [[Service Workers' Federation (CDLS)|Service Workers' Federation]] (Federazione Lavoratori dei Servizi)
