{{Politics of Liechtenstein}}
'''General elections''' were held in [[Liechtenstein]] between 9 and 11 February 2001. The result was a victory for the [[Progressive Citizens' Party in Liechtenstein|Progressive Citizens' Party]], which won 13 of the 25 seats in the [[Landtag of Liechtenstein|Landtag]]. Voter turnout was 86.72%.<ref name=NS/>
