{{Infobox airport | name = Yako Airport | IATA = | ICAO = DFCY | type = Public | city-served = [[Yako, Burkina Faso|Yako]] | location = {{flag|Burkina Faso}} | elevation-f = 984 | elevation-m = 300 | coordinates = {{coord|12|57|21|N|2|16|28|W|region:BF_type:airport|name=Yako Airport (Yako)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Burkina Faso | pushpin_label= DFCY | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Yako Airport in Burkina Faso | r1-number = Closed | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = | r1-surface = | footnotes = Sources: Landings.com<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?DFCY Airport record for Yako Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-08-22</ref> Google Maps<ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=12.9558333333333,-2.27438888888889+%28Yako+Airport%29|title=location of Yako Airport|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref> }}
'''Yako Airport''' {{Airport codes||DFCY}} was a public use [[airport]] located near [[Yako, Burkina Faso|Yako]], [[Passoré Province]], [[Burkina Faso]].
[[Google Earth Historical Imagery]] shows a {{convert|600|m}} dirt runway 07/25 at the listed coordinates in December 2001, but the area has since been built over with structures.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.com/maps/@12.9547018,-2.2758274,306m/data=!3m1!1e3|title=Google Maps|website=Google Maps|language=en|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
